14bfaf93-51e4-5e6a-b04d-86babe0e2c5d,tg:rubgr:1931,e73_Descriptions,,id.desc,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"

[vouwblad] In connection with Landscape with Sailing Boats & Burning Town: 1) Examine picture in Coll. Shapiro once more; 2) Establish for certain paintings by Cornelis Massys (form of signature etc): a. C. Bertin, signed CMF1543 [onleesbaar]); b. Antwerp signed CMA 1547 Urteil; c. drawings Brussels signed; [verso] Examine Gilles Mostaert e.g. Landscape with Christopher [onleesbaar] N° 1661 in 1911 catalogue p. 156 (repr. p. 155) as 'Niederländische Künstler um 1600' but according to Glück (probably correctly) in Art Quarterly, Winter 1950, p. 46, described as a copy after Gilles Mostaert (not repr. in 1929 reproductions).
